rows.label: qst002202_msg0001
rows.name: You're not like that girl, are you?

rows.label: qst002202_msg0002
rows.name: I guess I can tell you, then.

rows.label: qst002202_msg0003
rows.name:
There's this girl I've seen spying on
Mellica a lot lately. There were some
nasty-looking guys with her, too.

rows.label: qst002202_msg0004
rows.name:
I tried to get closer and find out what
she was up to, but she gave me the slip.

rows.label: qst002202_msg0005
rows.name:
Wish I could tell you more, but that's
all I've got.
